
1.  Install Webpack Node.js module:

    $ npm install webpack


2.  Install the 'babel-loader', 'babel-preset-es2015', and 'babel-preset-react' npm modules:

    $ npm install babel-loader

    ...

    $ npm install babel-preset-es2015

    ...

    $ npm install babel-preset-react


3.  Install the npm module 'babel-plugin-transform-object-rest-spread':

    $ npm install babel-plugin-transform-object-rest-spread


4.  Install the 'react' and 'react-dom' npm modules:

    $ npm install react

    ...

    $ npm install react-dom


5.  Install the 'redux' npm module:

    $ npm install redux


6.  Install the 'react-redux' npm module:

    $ npm install react-redux


7.  Install the npm module 'react-cookie':

... $ npm install react-cookie


8.  Compile JavaScript with Webpack:

    $ ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack.js --config ./webpack.config.js

